            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EHow%20proud%20and%20cocky%20are%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20oppress%20believers!%20Paul%20aptly%20describes%20their%20actions%3A%20%22Their%20talk%20is%20foul%2C%20like%20the%20stench%20from%20an%20open%20grave.%20Their%20speech%20is%20filled%20with%20lies.%20The%20poison%20of%20a%20deadly%20snake%20drips%20from%20their%20lips.%20Their%20mouths%20are%20full%20of%20cursing%20and%20bitterness.%20They%20are%20quick%20to%20commit%20murder%22%20(Romans%203%3A13-15).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EChristians%20need%20not%20worry%2C%20however%2C%20for%20the%20boasting%20of%20such%20evildoers%20against%20the%20righteous%20incites%20the%20Lord%20to%20action%3A%20%22Now%20I%20will%20rise%20up.%20.%20.%20.%22(Psalm%2012%3A5).%20God's%20remedy%20for%20persecuted%2C%20defeated%20believers%20is%20simply%20to%20supply%20them%20with%20the%20words%20of%20the%20Lord.%20God's%20Word%20is%20flawless%2C%20like%20%22silver%20refined%20in%20a%20furnace%2C%20purified%20seven%20times%20over%22%20(Psalm%2012%3A6).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20your%20battle%2C%20stop%20running%20to%20God%20to%20complain%20about%20your%20problem.%20Find%20His%20pure%20Word%20that%20He%20gave%20you%20to%20defeat%20your%20enemies%2C%20and%20rise%20up%20in%20victory%20over%20them.%20Others'%20advice%20may%20be%20helpful%2C%20but%20only%20the%20Word%20of%20God%20will%20put%20the%20devil%20to%20flight%2C%20as%20it%20is%20%22the%20sword%20of%20the%20Spirit%22%20(Ephesians%206%3A17).%20Employ%20the%20sword%20of%20God's%20Spirit%2C%20and%20watch%20your%20proud%20enemies%20flee%20in%20terror!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
