            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Chronicles.22:1-23:32",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Chronicles%2022%3A1-23%3A32%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20will%20be%20the%20location%20for%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20God%20and%20the%20place%20of%20the%20altar%20for%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20burnt%20offerings!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPreparations%20for%20the%20Temple%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20David%20gave%20orders%20to%20call%20together%20the%20foreigners%20living%20in%20Israel%2C%20and%20he%20assigned%20them%20the%20task%20of%20preparing%20finished%20stone%20for%20building%20the%20Temple%20of%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20provided%20large%20amounts%20of%20iron%20for%20the%20nails%20that%20would%20be%20needed%20for%20the%20doors%20in%20the%20gates%20and%20for%20the%20clamps%2C%20and%20he%20gave%20more%20bronze%20than%20could%20be%20weighed.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20also%20provided%20innumerable%20cedar%20logs%2C%20for%20the%20men%20of%20Tyre%20and%20Sidon%20had%20brought%20vast%20amounts%20of%20cedar%20to%20David.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20son%20Solomon%20is%20still%20young%20and%20inexperienced.%20And%20since%20the%20Temple%20to%20be%20built%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20must%20be%20a%20magnificent%20structure%2C%20famous%20and%20glorious%20throughout%20the%20world%2C%20I%20will%20begin%20making%20preparations%20for%20it%20now.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20David%20collected%20vast%20amounts%20of%20building%20materials%20before%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20sent%20for%20his%20son%20Solomon%20and%20instructed%20him%20to%20build%20a%20Temple%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_7%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BMy%20son%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20Temple%20to%20honor%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20told%20him.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_8%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20have%20killed%20many%20men%20in%20the%20battles%20you%20have%20fought.%20And%20since%20you%20have%20shed%20so%20much%20blood%20in%20my%20sight%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20the%20one%20to%20build%20a%20Temple%20to%20honor%20my%20name.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_9%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20will%20have%20a%20son%20who%20will%20be%20a%20man%20of%20peace.%20I%20will%20give%20him%20peace%20with%20his%20enemies%20in%20all%20the%20surrounding%20lands.%20His%20name%20will%20be%20Solomon%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E22%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3ESolomon%3C%2Fem%3E%20sounds%20like%20and%20is%20probably%20derived%20from%20the%20Hebrew%20word%20for%20%26%23x201C%3Bpeace.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20I%20will%20give%20peace%20and%20quiet%20to%20Israel%20during%20his%20reign.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_10%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20is%20the%20one%20who%20will%20build%20a%20Temple%20to%20honor%20my%20name.%20He%20will%20be%20my%20son%2C%20and%20I%20will%20be%20his%20father.%20And%20I%20will%20secure%20the%20throne%20of%20his%20kingdom%20over%20Israel%20forever.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_11%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%2C%20my%20son%2C%20may%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20be%20with%20you%20and%20give%20you%20success%20as%20you%20follow%20his%20directions%20in%20building%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_12%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20may%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20give%20you%20wisdom%20and%20understanding%2C%20that%20you%20may%20obey%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20as%20you%20rule%20over%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_13%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20you%20will%20be%20successful%20if%20you%20carefully%20obey%20the%20decrees%20and%20regulations%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20to%20Israel%20through%20Moses.%20Be%20strong%20and%20courageous%3B%20do%20not%20be%20afraid%20or%20lose%20heart!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_14%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20provide%20materials%20for%20building%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2014%3Bnearly%204%2C000%20tons%20of%20gold%2C%2040%2C000%20tons%20of%20silver%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E22%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E100%2C000%20talents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B3%2C400%20metric%20tons%5D%20%3Cem%3Eof%20gold%2C%201%2C000%2C000%20talents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B34%2C000%20metric%20tons%5D%20%3Cem%3Eof%20silver.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20so%20much%20iron%20and%20bronze%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20weighed.%20I%20have%20also%20gathered%20timber%20and%20stone%20for%20the%20walls%2C%20though%20you%20may%20need%20to%20add%20more.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_15%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20a%20large%20number%20of%20skilled%20stonemasons%20and%20carpenters%20and%20craftsmen%20of%20every%20kind.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_16%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20expert%20goldsmiths%20and%20silversmiths%20and%20workers%20of%20bronze%20and%20iron.%20Now%20begin%20the%20work%2C%20and%20may%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20be%20with%20you!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_17%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20ordered%20all%20the%20leaders%20of%20Israel%20to%20assist%20Solomon%20in%20this%20project.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_18%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20is%20with%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20declared.%20%26%23x201C%3BHe%20has%20given%20you%20peace%20with%20the%20surrounding%20nations.%20He%20has%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20me%2C%20and%20they%20are%20now%20subject%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20his%20people.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_22_19%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20seek%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20with%20all%20your%20heart%20and%20soul.%20Build%20the%20sanctuary%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20God%20so%20that%20you%20can%20bring%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20and%20the%20holy%20vessels%20of%20God%20into%20the%20Temple%20built%20to%20honor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20name.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDuties%20of%20the%20Levites%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20David%20was%20an%20old%20man%2C%20he%20appointed%20his%20son%20Solomon%20to%20be%20king%20over%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20summoned%20all%20the%20leaders%20of%20Israel%2C%20together%20with%20the%20priests%20and%20Levites.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20the%20Levites%20who%20were%20thirty%20years%20old%20or%20older%20were%20counted%2C%20and%20the%20total%20came%20to%2038%2C000.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BFrom%20all%20the%20Levites%2C%2024%2C000%20will%20supervise%20the%20work%20at%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Another%206%2C000%20will%20serve%20as%20officials%20and%20judges.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAnother%204%2C000%20will%20work%20as%20gatekeepers%2C%20and%204%2C000%20will%20praise%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20with%20the%20musical%20instruments%20I%20have%20made.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20divided%20the%20Levites%20into%20divisions%20named%20after%20the%20clans%20descended%20from%20the%20three%20sons%20of%20Levi%26%23x2014%3BGershon%2C%20Kohath%2C%20and%20Merari.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_23_7%22%20bk%3D%2